reviews.review_text:
Upgrade!!! Hampton 1987 - Smoking 1st Night of the East Coast Spring Tour Yes!! 

Been waiting for this one for close to 33 years. 
Thank you Don Pearson & Charlie Miller! 

I've wanted a good soundboard of this show ever since seeing it, but sadly it never materialized.. until now! 

Prior to '87 we were getting all those crispy '85 SBDs. So when I got home from tour, I started looking around, and waiting for a crispy SBD of these three amazing nights in Hampton, and waiting, and waiting, and waiting...

Just recently Charlie started circulating these sweet tapes recorded by Don Pearson, and today is the day. 1st Night of Hampton '87! 

I still wish there were straight SBDs circulating around of these 3 shows, but since those don't appear to circulate / exist (Healy tested out his Ambient Mics & UltraMatrix scene on most of the SBDs from the Spring Tour and 1987 in general) this is definitely the next best thing!

For all three nights the energy in the "spaceship" was off the hook and the shows were nothing short of magical, Jerry was back and we were all so thrilled to get to enjoy the ride for a little bit longer. 

Never Had Such A Good Time, In My Life Before! 

Here we are in 2019 and this is by far the best source of this show to turn up yet. If you've been looking for this show, get this, if you don't know about it, get this. 

Now Charlie, where are the Alpine '87 SBDs?!?!

It's Miller Time, thanks Charlie!
